001package ca.gc.cra.radar.domain.protocol;
002
003/**
004 * Known application protocols handled by RADAR.
005 *
006 * @since RADAR 0.1-doc
007 */
008public enum ProtocolId {
009  /** Hypertext Transfer Protocol. */
010  HTTP,
011  /** IBM 3270 terminal protocol transported over TN3270. */
012  TN3270,
013  /** Fallback when protocol detection is inconclusive. */
014  UNKNOWN
015}
